{"tid":1862343,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(冇口罩入)自製口罩材料介紹","createTime":"2020-02-04T14:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T14:45:50.000Z","uid":326037,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9a1d64eb32cee3be6a0e5d27f7b03fca04b208","tid":1862343,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"之前睇到有人講用濾網可製口罩，出去揾到3M有出隻靜電空氣濾網，可過濾PM2.5、花粉、細菌、煙霧等，而飛沫係5微米都應該濾到，咁即係同口罩冇分別，我見到係實惠有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcYPyYT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcYPyYT.png&h=add8a0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未證實有冇效，冇口罩可試下，但不論有冇效藍屍都唔好學<br />\n<br />\n覺得有用請睇晒下面文宣再轉貼出去 <br />\n<br />\n光復香港 榮光自由<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVq2TZi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVq2TZi.png&h=91c4e7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KbEWcD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KbEWcD.png&h=c858b9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/USmtPxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUSmtPxD.png&h=9875258c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmSs45Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmSs45Z.png&h=d4948ad3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}